description: The delectable Japanese cuisine at Dobi’s Teriyaki is the talk of Missoula. And when you get a taste of all the delicious flavors you find at this terrific truck, alongside their famously fantastic service, you’ll understand why. Local folks love the teriyaki (both regular and spicy), so make your way right to Dobi’s Teriyaki and after a delightful time, you’ll be sure to have such a “rice day”!
name: Dobi's Teriyaki
